Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:08.36,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Once there was a man who obtained everything,\Nthe legendary Pirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:12.91,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,His last words before he was executed inspired people to sail the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:14.63,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,All my wealth and treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.27,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,It can be yours if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.42,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Search for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:19.79,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything in that one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:22.82,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,People now set sail in search of romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:25.40,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The world has entered a Great Age of Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:40.01,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,All pirates who seek One Piece\Nstrive to reach the second half of the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:42.51,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The place called the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:51.23,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,However, the only one who ever conquered that ocean\Nwas the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:57.44,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has killed\Nthe dreams and ambitions of countless pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:03.41,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the boy who ate the Gomu Gomu Fruit\Nand became a rubber man,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:07.16,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nare going to challenge that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:11.74,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:16.88,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,In order to reach their next stage, the New World, Luffy and the other Straw Hat Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:21.85,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,have gone to Fishman Island,\Nlocated ten thousand meters under the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:27.92,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,But there, the New Fishman Pirates\Nare planning to overthrow the Ryuuguu Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:31.92,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and Vander Decken has been stalking the Mermaid Princess Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:35.77,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The crew find themselves drawn into these events.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:41.70,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro, Usopp and Brook have been captured by Hody in Ryuuguu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.45,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,My love was unrequited...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:44.82,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unrequited!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:47.17,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:53.50,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:58.66,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,I know!  I just have to destroy everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:03:59.84,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,Every last thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:05.59,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... You've caused me so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:08.72,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Hachi for me, Caimie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:09.89,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.98,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Megalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:22.28,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... the power of their drugs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:46.36,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost at the plaza.  Hurry, Megalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.55,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:52.05,Main,Totally The Real Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it is me -jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:54.14,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Jinbe-sama!  Megalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.94,Main,Totally The Real Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it is me -jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.32,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,You're alright after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.82,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.44,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.33,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,No!  Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:13.49,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.56,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop! { def: please don't! }
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:24.03,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:29.89,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still, unless you want the princess to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:32.18,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:35.85,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's get going with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.49,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:52.54,Main,Zeo,0000,0000,0000,,Our gallery has grown quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:58.12,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:01.84,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this is a nice view!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.38,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Manboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:08.22,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Ryuuboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.14,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Fukaboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:13.26,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,What did those pirates do? {Literally "the subordinates of that pirate crew", but that strikes me as kind of redundant.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:16.60,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,The Princes were wiping the floor with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:20.23,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,But then the situation suddenly turned on its head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:23.49,Main,Dosun,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't rampaged enough -zugon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:27.04,Main,Ikaros,0000,0000,0000,,Muhi, you're too fired up!\NYou're gonna turn me into a grilled squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:32.93,Main,Zeo,0000,0000,0000,,The army's soldiers, the ministers, and the Royal Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:37.08,Main,Zeo,0000,0000,0000,,Now, there's nobody left in the country\Nwho can fight us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:39.83,Main,Manboshi,0000,0000,0000,,What outrageous power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.18,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:47.10,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!  Their power isn't real -jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.68,Main,Ryuuboshi,0000,0000,0000,,But they can still use it\Nto take the country from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:52.20,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hody, let's execute them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.28,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Roast them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:54.56,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,No, skewer them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:59.87,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Those royals wanted to coexist with the humans!\NThey have no pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:00.97,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Give them a cruel death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.86,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Put them up for display at the gallery!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.36,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Execute them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:16.99,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Execute them!  Execute them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.77,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Execute them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:20.08,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:29.62,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Decken's crew still haven't\Nsent word that Shirahoshi is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:35.39,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't lure her here, this will all be meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:40.24,Main,Manboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your hands off our sister!  She's not a warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:42.90,Main,Manboshi,0000,0000,0000,,What threat does she pose to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:47.52,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.43,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,The one I want to get rid of the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:56.53,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,is the legendary mermaid,\Nwho possesses that most troublesome power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:57.79,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:00.62,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:03.71,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,We've caught them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:14.02,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Shirahoshi and Jinbe fell for our trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:16.40,Main,Princes,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:19.22,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Father!  Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:21.80,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,What luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:29.30,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,The two people I feared the most, captured at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:32.74,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,This is almost too good to be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.55,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,I really am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:41.50,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I fell for their trap, even you ended up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.50,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,What's done is done.  Don't worry about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:47.29,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,So you came after all, Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:52.30,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I used to like you,\Nback when you were more ruthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:57.93,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you, Hody?  You look different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.78,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,It's Boss Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:03.06,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he left the island after he resigned from the Seven Warlords of the Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:08.04,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Princess Shirahoshi\Nhad been kidnapped by Straw Hat Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:10.65,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Did Boss Jinbe rescue her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:16.14,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we have everyone we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:19.00,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,It was much easier than I thought it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:25.61,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the only ones left are the Straw Hats, and I don't know what they'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:32.13,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing that they're at a loss,\Nlooking for a way inside Ryuuguu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:36.30,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they come here,\Nenraged by the death of their companions...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:40.89,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be ready for them. { def: is there a way to tweak this line to match his speech pattern? }
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:18.16,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I've been capturing human slaves\Non the ocean floor for the past month...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.76,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty thousand of them! {...Seriously? THIRTY THOUSAND in the past month? Is he really saying that an average of a thousand people travel to Fishman Island daily? :/}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:33.40,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,And seventy thousand fishmen, all heavily armed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.34,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:09.48,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,They've moved here from the closed-off Fishman District.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:17.20,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,In all, we've got a hundred thousand outlaws!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:55.77,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,There are some women and children around the plaza, but they can't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:59.03,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take care of them after things have settled down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:03.86,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the number of human slaves\Nwill rapidly grow soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.91,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,But for now,\Nwe have a hundred thousand new citizens!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:12.16,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who have disgraced our species\Nwill be forced to surrender their houses to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:17.93,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Die or run away... They should decide quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:21.96,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,You're causing quite a ruckus out here in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:25.18,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,How undignified.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:28.19,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't let yourself get carried away like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:32.22,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Hody Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:34.27,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Long time, no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:37.19,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:42.52,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to say something to you,\Nsince you seem to think you've already won.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.91,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Madame Shyarly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:49.46,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that a certain man\Nwould destroy Fishman Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:52.04,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,in my predictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:55.67,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,We might end up destroying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:58.42,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,So you saw me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:01.73,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:06.01,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,The man I saw destroying the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:08.85,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,was Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.77,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:17.90,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,What will the boy with the straw hat do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:20.61,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can't be sure, but{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.82,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.82,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,That it won't be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:28.20,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,One thing is certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:31.71,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody holds the fate\Nof Fishman Island in their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:34.63,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,But Hody, I know this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:36.34,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,It is not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:41.02,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,I see!  Madame's predictions are never wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:45.18,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nthe future where Hody reigns over this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:46.55,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,has no chance of happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:10.29,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Madame Shyarly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.46,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:35.52,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,How could he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:41.22,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous.  What were you implying, Shyarly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:42.27,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to get back at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:48.03,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I'm different from your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:55.73,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,True, when I was a kid, everyone in\NFishman District looked up to your brother, Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:15:01.21,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,But we have gained power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:08.93,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,By now, the mark of the Arlong Pirates is just an empty symbol to unite us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:12.43,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong's name is completely unnecessary now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:19.94,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who can crush this country down to its foundation, and recreate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:22.49,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:25.23,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I have the power to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:30.44,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, the size of this mob!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:33.64,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,This is my strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:40.83,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,My plan has been in the works for ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:43.09,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:49.21,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,who killed the beloved Queen of Ryuuguu Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:57.35,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Your beloved Otohime was killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:00.10,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,by me! {WHAT A TWEEST!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.57,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:14.16,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.83,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.83,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,what about that human?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:23.66,Main,Daruma,0000,0000,0000,,You're fools for not realizing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:28.42,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,A few days before that day ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:37.43,Flashbacks,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are,\Nbut if the pay's good, I'll gladly take any job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.88,Flashbacks,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:45.02,Flashbacks,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,That's half of your payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:47.77,Flashbacks,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the rest after you've finished the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:50.69,Flashbacks,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:54.48,Flashbacks,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Even this is enough to keep me drinking for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.83,Flashbacks,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,So?  What kind of job is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:03.50,Flashbacks,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,It's an easy job.  Even a kid could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:08.21,Flashbacks,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to make sure that nobody notices you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:13.34,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,And then, on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:26.69,Flashbacks,Warrior,0000,0000,0000,,Get back!  They're going up in flames! {Copy-paste from 546. Just this line. For some reason the rest of them appear to be different from that episode...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:27.92,Flashbacks,Warrior,0000,0000,0000,,Put out the flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:28.66,Flashbacks,Warrior,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:30.17,Flashbacks,Warrior,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the Royal Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:32.20,Flashbacks,Warrior,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and put out the flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:47.12,Flashbacks,Warrior,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama's been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:51.42,Flashbacks,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Give me the rest of my money already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:54.92,Flashbacks,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,I burned the signatures, just like I promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:58.21,Flashbacks,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,I won't bother you after this, so just give me the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:06.04,Flashbacks,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:08.78,Flashbacks,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,You foolish human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:11.19,Flashbacks,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Damn it to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:21.74,Flashbacks,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,A human... {Copy-paste from 547}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:26.75,Flashbacks,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,killed our country's queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:34.07,Flashbacks,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime's killer was human! {End copy-paste from 547}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:42.51,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Every single one of you was tricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.89,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!  So he...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:48.44,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:51.54,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Hody, you filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:57.68,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:58.95,Main,Ryuuboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:01.15,Main,Manboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.42,Main,Ryuuboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.87,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,She was quite a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:12.15,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Shirahoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:16.00,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Claiming that revenge against humans was evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:20.51,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Preaching all around the island\Nthat we should get along with humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:24.26,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,And that woman almost realized her dreams.\NI hated every single thing about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:28.48,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,No, she was the kind of person whose influence wouldn't fade even if I killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:32.69,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,But to me, your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:36.32,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,was someone who just had to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:38.65,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!  Stop hurting the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:40.07,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,This is too cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:46.95,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Since I couldn't just kill her...\NI made an excellent plan to turn her death to my favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:53.29,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,To renew Fishman Island's hatred toward humankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:58.04,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,and to break that ridiculous dream Otohime and the citizens shared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:03.61,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them shattered in an instant!  It was a flawless plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:10.19,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Namely, to have a human kill Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:19.90,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,If I blamed the humans, the citizens' hatred toward humankind would flare up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:26.90,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,And you all fell completely\Nfor the scenario that I set up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:32.55,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,It truly was worth killing her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:34.86,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,You hear that, Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:39.28,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,It was not some human that killed your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:44.72,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,It was me, a fellow fishman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:51.83,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I, the very person before your eyes, was the one who killed her! {Say, I'm getting the distinct impression that Hody may have been the one who killed Otohime. Does anyone else get that impression or is it just me?}{ def: i'm not sure.  he seems to be hinting at it }
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:09.74,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:11.95,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.93,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:31.28,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,They say the people of Fishman Island\Nbuilt this mysterious giant ship long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:32.88,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,It's called Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:38.65,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why this ship was built...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.99,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,but by now it's just a relic of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:44.19,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just touch it with my right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:47.78,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Decken... W-What are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:02.70,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?  What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:08.27,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,My heartache from being rejected will never fade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:11.44,Main,Wadatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:21.32,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It started moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.32,0:22:23.25,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:24.35,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:30.39,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,I sent Noah flying straight toward Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.39,0:22:31.75,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:35.10,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Noah is half the size of Fishman Island itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.10,0:22:37.94,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, if Noah collides with the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:40.87,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,it won't just kill Shirahoshi,\Nit'll make the entire island crumble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:44.46,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,There is nowhere to run or hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:50.08,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi will live in my heart for all time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:53.15,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,May the entire island perish!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:55.98,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, my beloved Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:59.72,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:11.03,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi desperately tries to\Nkeep her promise with her mother Otohime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:16.64,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Hody, who taunts her,\Nfinally begins Neptune's execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:21.96,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The people are trapped in an abyss of despair,\Nand shout the name of their last remaining hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:26.17,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Their voices echo across all of Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:27.55,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:28.67,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi's Tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:30.93,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy Finally Arrives
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:32.66,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
